      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study with at least three systematically refined grids; GCI < 5% on the primary QoI (relative hemolysis index). Required level 2 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted using grids of 2.1M, 5.8M, and 14.2M cells. The Grid Convergence Index for the relative hemolysis index was 2.3%, well below the 5% threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence. Achieved level 3 exceeds the requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
