      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., validation metric V) must be computed between CFD predictions and experimental data for the primary QoI. Required level 2 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index predicted by CFD (RH = 0.81) is compared against the experimental reference (RH_ref = 0.85) using the validation metric V. The normalized error of 4.7% is within the experimental uncertainty band of ±8%. Achieved level 2 meets the requirement."
    },
    {
