      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index is the primary regulatory QoI for CPB device hemolysis assessment. CFD-predicted shear stress distributions and exposure time integrals are the direct inputs to the hemolysis power-law model. The validation QoIs are identical to the COU decision QoIs. Achieved level 2 meets the requirement."
