    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the device does not produce hemolysis exceeding the predicate device under worst-case operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index of 0.81 satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion with adequate margin. The overall credibility evidence package is judged sufficient for a Medium assurance level Class II device submission.",
